meta.desc: Converts SACD image files, Philips DSDIFF and Sony DSF files to 24-bit high resolution wave files. Handles both DST and DSD streams.
meta.desc_long:
Super Audio CD decoder. Converts SACD image files, Philips DSDIFF and Sony DSF files to 24-bit high resolution wave files.
Handles both DST and DSD streams.
